She over heard Starscreams words on her link. She frowned,"HUSH! I am 
in a meeting. We can talk later."



--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, minime_316@h... wrote:
> Starscream
> 
> Starscream watched them walk off. He was angry. Even if this bot 
> didn't know where Megatron was, she must have known something. Why 
> did Inferno want her to go to Arachnia when he worked for Megatron? 
> It made no sense! Unless.....By the Matrix! That's it! Megatron's 
> goal was to untie the Preds, and he must have made a treaty with 
> Arachnia! Now she comes in here and merges groups and sends all our 
> plans to Megatron! She must be stopped! Starscream left and burst 
> into the conference room.
> 
> "KitKat, stop! Arachnia is a fraud! She is working for Megatron!"
